      • fetchFiles

        public java.util.List<java.io.File> fetchFiles()
                                        throws java.io.IOException
        Fetch all relevant csv files and the "dates.txt" file from the semester's directory. The directory is a system path. Each csv file is put into the csvFiles list. If the file doesn't exist, or any other issue is encountered, an IOException is thrown.
        Returns:
        List of fetched csv files
        Throws:
